<Layout title="Toronto Airbnb Host Blog - Tips, Regulations & Guides" description="Expert guides for Toronto & GTA Airbnb hosts. STR regulations, hosting tips, revenue optimization, and industry news. Everything you need to succeed as a short-term rental host." schema={blogSchema}>
